`@csrf_exempt` tells your view to not look for `csrf_token` although the website requires one. Remove `@csrf_exempt` from your view and pass in your form in your template a `{% csrf_token %}` i.e.

    &lt;form action=&#39;/login&#39; method=&#39;POST&#39;&gt;
        {% csrf_token %}
        &lt;input type=&#39;text&#39; name=&#39;username&#39;/&gt;
        &lt;input type=&#39;password&#39; name=&#39;password&#39;/&gt;
    &lt;/form&gt;

